snippet.title: Baca - Amstrad CPC Homebrew
snippet.description:
One of the pretty old Amstrad CPC homebrew games released to the public domain, released in 1998. Baca is essentially a Columns clone, but with letters instead of jewels. There isn't much to find online as far as information is concerned.
